# TSOFT Tailwind Twig Section

TSOFT Figma to Twig section/snippet workflow.

Use $tsoft-design-to-twig for Twig work in section, snippets, and related assets.
Detect target path, read matching references, then apply figma/global rules while
preserving theme hooks and responsive Tailwind structure.

Core constraints:
- Keep existing `data-*` attributes, macros, and snippet include flow.
- Reuse semantic theme classes (`bg-primary`, `text-body`, `border-form`); avoid arbitrary values.
- Use `container` and Tailwind defaults; avoid fixed max-width literals unless required.
- Apply responsive layout primarily with `lg` breakpoint.
